         "title":"Example: DBSCAN on the Two Moons Dataset",
         "bullets":[
            {"text":"The two moons dataset is a classic example of a dataset with complex cluster shapes","source_id":"Page 204"},
            {"text":"DBSCAN can capture the two half-circles and separate them using the default settings","source_id":"Page 204"},
            {"text":"The algorithm produces the desired number of clusters (two) with the default parameter settings","source_id":"Page 204"}
         ],
         "key_message":"DBSCAN can effectively capture complex cluster shapes, such as the two moons dataset.",
         "visual_hint":"comparison",
